it.

21:09.335 --> 21:19.044 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: Reaction was
swift. Muslim students
walked out of St. Cloud Tech in
spring 2015.

21:19.078 --> 21:24.483 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Reports of harassment emerged in
other cities
throughout summer and fall of
last year, especially

21:24.517 --> 21:29.255 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
