21:39.698 --> 21:43.802 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: The president
addressed the
problem at his first ever visit
to a mosque

21:43.836 --> 21:45.471 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in February.

21:45.504 --> 21:48.174 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
BARACK OBAMA: We are one
