our nation.

21:54.513 --> 21:56.382 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(APPLAUSE)

21:56.415 --> 22:01.053 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN: We're coming together to
create a difference
in your school, so everybody in
the school

22:01.086 --> 22:02.821 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
