used the year since the walkout
to speak out

22:06.592 --> 22:12.231 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
against harassment by training
this specially
chosen group of students to go
out and begin

22:12.264 --> 22:13.999 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
a dialogue with the bullies.

22:14.033 --> 22:17.403 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
UBAH NOOR, Student: We're trying
to include
people, and we're not going to
sit here and

22:17.436 --> 22:20.539 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
