arranged themselves
according to how far they were
born from St.

22:38.224 --> 22:39.558 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Cloud.

22:39.592 --> 22:41.994 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Staff member Sebastian
Witherspoon is one
of the group's founders.

22:42.027 --> 22:44.063 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What do you want them to learn?

22:44.096 --> 22:47.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEBASTIAN WITHERSPOON, St. Cloud
Area School
District: Difference is OK. If
you're from

22:47.866 --> 22:50.970 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Somalia, if you're from Duluth
as a black
male, if you're from
Robbinsdale, whatever,

22:51.003 --> 22:55.908 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
