There's beauty
in coming from different places,
being different

22:55.941 --> 22:57.710 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
culture, have different
ethnicities.

22:57.743 --> 23:02.648 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That's -- to me, that's --
there's education
to me, is having all these
people who have

23:02.681 --> 23:06.785 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a variety of experiences and us
learning from
that to enrich our lives.

23:06.819 --> 23:12.091 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: Students are also
organizing
a cultural carnival, featuring
food, music,

23:12.124 --> 23:16.729 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
