23:18.631 --> 23:21.267 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STUDENT: The people who don't
want to be there
are the people that need to be
there. I mean,

23:21.300 --> 23:24.937 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I feel like the people who need
the conversation
aren't the ones that are
actually coming.

23:24.970 --> 23:29.008 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: There could be
another approach,
which the president had seemed
to use, and

23:29.041 --> 23:30.876 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
we brought it up with Hafsa.

23:30.909 --> 23:37.549 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Hafsa, I'm wondering maybe the
better approach
would be to educate those
bullies about what

23:37.583 --> 23:39.418 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
it means to be an American.

23:39.451 --> 23:45.424 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HAFSA ABDI: Mm-hmm. I do feel
like it comes
from the stereotype of what an
American looks

23:45.457 --> 23:50.396 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
like. So, a lot of people feel
someone who
looks like me can't be an
American, because

23:50.429 --> 23:56.001 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of my skin color or like a hijab
that I'm
wearing, and that makes me not
American.

23:56.035 --> 23:59.371 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So I feel like really actually
do need to
understand the actual definition
of what it

23:59.405 --> 24:00.539 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
is to be an American.

24:00.572 --> 24:03.609 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: But others in the
group weren't
so sure.

24:03.642 --> 24:05.411 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
What about the notion of
America?

24:05.444 --> 24:09.882 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
UBAH NOOR: I feel like we have
been teaching
what our country has been
founded on since

24:09.915 --> 24:13.952 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
