position.

32:16.768 --> 32:18.670 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MDNM /THE MOST REVEREND MICHAEL
CURRY: Thank
you for that.

32:18.703 --> 32:23.008 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Let me ask you
first, how would
you describe the place that the
Episcopal

32:23.041 --> 32:28.713 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Church occupies in the broad
religious profile
