now?

32:28.747 --> 32:32.250 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MDNM /THE MOST REVEREND MICHAEL
CURRY: The
Episcopal Church probably
represents a moderate

32:32.284 --> 32:37.088 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
