32:43.161 --> 32:47.265 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
now we're seeing the live that
out in some
new ways that -- to be a church
that really

32:47.299 --> 32:53.905 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
can embrace diverse, not only
theological
traditions or liturgical and
worship styles

32:53.939 --> 32:57.509 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
