Episcopal
Church and the Anglican way at
its best.

33:01.680 --> 33:07.152 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You're now six
months into
this position. How has the fact
that you are

33:07.185 --> 33:13.358 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
