33:18.964 --> 33:24.169 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MDNM /THE MOST REVEREND MICHAEL
CURRY: Certainly,
that has affected, only in the
sense that

33:24.202 --> 33:29.507 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
it is a first. Beyond that, I
have a funny
feeling I was probably elected
for a variety

33:29.541 --> 33:31.309 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of reasons.

33:31.343 --> 33:38.783 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I suspect that my election was a
moment of
hope that we could begin to help
the Episcopal

33:38.817 --> 33:45.357 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Church and Episcopalians begin
to focus outward
