33:53.064 --> 33:58.069 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that's a game-changer, in
and of itself,
the various forms and ways we're
divided between

33:58.103 --> 34:06.077 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
each other, whether it is racial
or socioeconomic
