of reconciliation

34:12.384 --> 34:14.619 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in this world.

34:14.653 --> 34:21.693 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That really does have something
to do with
helping the world stop living a
nightmare

34:21.726 --> 34:28.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and start living something
closer to God's
dream. And that's worth doing.
And I have

34:28.300 --> 34:30.101 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
