elected.

34:30.135 --> 34:36.041 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You have spoken a
great deal
and preached about social
justice in its many

34:36.074 --> 34:37.842 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
