transformative for themselves
and for the world. And, as a
result, the earliest

35:16.815 --> 35:22.821 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Christian communities were
communities where
both slave and free coexisted
and lived together,

35:22.854 --> 35:30.996 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
