and Greek or
Gentile coexisted and lived
together.

35:31.029 --> 35:36.267 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That was the earliest Christian
movement.
And I'm committed to helping the
Episcopal

35:36.301 --> 35:41.940 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Church become a Jesus movement
today that
helps the society live into a
vision.

35:41.973 --> 35:45.510 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: What's the
practical effect
of that? I mean, how would
people's lives

35:45.543 --> 35:46.911 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
change as a result of that,
ideally?

35:46.945 --> 35:49.514 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MDNM /THE MOST REVEREND MICHAEL
CURRY: I
think dramatically.

35:49.547 --> 35:55.720 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Imagine if just Episcopalians
were practically
living their daily lives as
reflections of

35:55.754 --> 36:01.626 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the way Jesus of Nazareth lived
his, loving
in the same way that Jesus did
and does, giving

36:01.659 --> 36:07.332 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in the same way, forgiving,
doing justice,
caring, living compassionate
lives.

36:07.365 --> 36:12.270 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
I have a funny feeling
Episcopalians could
be transformative both in our
interpersonal

36:12.303 --> 36:17.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
relationships and in our social
and political
relationships. What would happen
if Christians

36:17.976 --> 36:24.282 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
just acted like Christians? It
would change
our politics. It would change
our social order.

36:24.315 --> 36:26.284 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It could change our global
community.

36:26.317 --> 36:28.420 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Do you think our
politics needs
changing?

36:28.453 --> 36:30.855 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MDNM /THE MOST REVEREND MICHAEL
CURRY: Regardless
of which side of the aisle
you're on -- this

36:30.889 --> 36:36.761 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
