unenlightened
self-interest, but from the
perspective of

36:41.933 --> 36:46.004 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
our interests, the common good,
the common
wheel.

36:46.037 --> 36:53.044 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Imagine our global politics.
Imagine our economic
relationships. It's
world-changing. And I

36:53.078 --> 36:56.481 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
happen to believe that the way
of Jesus of
Nazareth -- I'm not talking
about everybody

36:56.514 --> 37:00.085 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
having to become an
Episcopalian, although
that would be nice -- but that's
not what

37:00.118 --> 37:01.853 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I'm really talking about.

37:01.886 --> 37:07.325 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I'm talking about a way of
living that is
deeply grounded in the kind of
love that is

37:07.358 --> 37:13.998 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
