Valentine's Day, but
that is a way of living in this
world and

37:14.032 --> 37:15.834 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
engaging it.

37:15.867 --> 37:18.403 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Finally, Isaiah got caught up
like in the
spirit, like a Episcopalian in a
Baptist church,

37:18.436 --> 37:20.305 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
got caught up in the spirit.

37:20.338 --> 37:27.245 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: They say that
Sunday morning
is the most segregated time and
place in American

37:27.278 --> 37:31.583 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
