country. Should
that change?

37:31.616 --> 37:37.722 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MDNM /THE MOST REVEREND MICHAEL
CURRY: I
think the church can create
space for authentic

37:37.755 --> 37:43.294 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ethnic congregations that
