need, especially at a particular
time.

37:43.328 --> 37:49.567 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But it must also move into
inhabiting or creating
space for congregations where
people of different

37:49.601 --> 37:55.874 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
races and ethnic backgrounds and
socioeconomic
classes actually come together,
because, ultimately,

37:55.907 --> 38:04.883 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I mean, I do pray for the day
when those of
us who have the same commitment
to follow

38:04.916 --> 38:10.121 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the way of Jesus of Nazareth can
actually
find that that is our primal
commitment, and

38:10.155 --> 38:12.891 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that, in Christ, there is no
hindrances.

38:12.924 --> 38:16.060 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In Christ, there is east nor
west, in him,
no south nor north.

38:16.094 --> 38:20.565 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We are going to get there. And I
pray for
that day and have worked for
that day, but

38:20.598 --> 38:26.905 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I know that, between here and
there, we have
to approximate it as best we
can.

38:26.938 --> 38:32.477 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: We have learned
just recently
that Pope Francis is saying that
he is open

38:32.510 --> 38:39.350 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
