38:46.324 --> 38:48.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MDNM /THE MOST REVEREND MICHAEL
CURRY: When
we finally get to the point of
saying, who

38:48.960 --> 38:54.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
has God called to be a bishop or
