when we're all
apart.

39:32.637 --> 39:37.442 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I -- you know, my Catholic
brothers and
sisters, you have to make your
decision as

39:37.475 --> 39:44.649 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
