39:58.396 --> 40:00.999 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MDNM /THE MOST REVEREND MICHAEL
CURRY: We
have a better Episcopal Church.
I have been

40:01.032 --> 40:06.437 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
