40:08.406 --> 40:12.310 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Presiding Bishop
Michael Curry,
thank you very much.

40:12.343 --> 40:20.518 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MDNM /THE MOST REVEREND MICHAEL
CURRY: Thank
you. God bless you.

