they're eggs or
larvae.

42:02.754 --> 42:07.492 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: Grosboll and a team of
other government
scientists are now working to
boost the numbers

42:07.525 --> 42:13.431 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
