42:15.233 --> 42:20.972 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAN GROSBOLL: The base is here
in order to
support troops training, so the
troops are

42:21.005 --> 42:27.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
