that we also
can provide habitat for
endangered species

42:27.245 --> 42:32.583 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is a really good thing, but it's
important
that all of the preservation of
endangered

42:32.617 --> 42:35.720 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
species is not borne by the
base.

